OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe far
OL,6,Fnorthwest including Lewis and the
OL,7,FNorth Coast of Highland staying cloudy
OL,8,Fwith occasional mainly light rain this
OL,9,Fevening, becoming dry overnight.
OL,10,FElsewhere some good clear spells
OL,11,Fovernight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA generally dry bright day
OL,14,Fwith some good sunny spells and
OL,15,Fbecoming very warm. The Isles will
OL,16,Fcloud over towards evening with some
OL,17,Flight rain and mist.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
