OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart in west on Wednesday, burning
OL,7,Foff then some sunshine, very warm.
OL,8,FThursday bright and very warm or hot
OL,9,Fthen some thundery showers. Less warm,
OL,10,Fshowery on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
